{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1912,"text":"On November 5th, 1990,"},{"time":4333,"text":"a man named El-Sayyid Nosair walked"},{"time":7132,"text":"into a hotel in Manhattan"},{"time":9517,"text":"and assassinated Rabbi Meir Kahane,"},{"time":12482,"text":"the leader of the Jewish Defense League."},{"time":16280,"text":"Nosair was initially found not guilty of the murder,"},{"time":18940,"text":"but while serving time on lesser charges,"},{"time":22566,"text":"he and other men began planning attacks"},{"time":25160,"text":"on a dozen New York City landmarks,"},{"time":27051,"text":"including tunnels, synagogues"},{"time":29395,"text":"and the United Nations headquarters."},{"time":32281,"text":"Thankfully, those plans were foiled"},{"time":34004,"text":"by an FBI informant."},{"time":36841,"text":"Sadly, the 1993 bombing"},{"time":39397,"text":"of the World Trade Center was not."},{"time":42578,"text":"Nosair would eventually be convicted"},{"time":44317,"text":"for his involvement in the plot."},{"time":47741,"text":"El-Sayyid Nosair is my father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51988,"text":"I was born in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania"},{"time":53898,"text":"in 1983 to him, an Egyptian engineer,"},{"time":57622,"text":"and a loving American mother\nand grade school teacher,"},{"time":60817,"text":"who together tried their best"},{"time":62068,"text":"to create a happy childhood for me."},{"time":65181,"text":"It wasn't until I was seven years old"},{"time":66723,"text":"that our family dynamic started to change."},{"time":70266,"text":"My father exposed me to a side of Islam"},{"time":73416,"text":"that few people, including the majority of Muslims,"},{"time":76343,"text":"get to see."},{"time":79060,"text":"It's been my experience that when people"},{"time":80729,"text":"take the time to interact with one another,"},{"time":83091,"text":"it doesn't take long to realize that for the most part,"},{"time":86149,"text":"we all want the same things out of life."},{"time":88601,"text":"However, in every religion, in every population,"},{"time":91778,"text":"you'll find a small percentage of people"},{"time":94366,"text":"who hold so fervently to their beliefs"},{"time":97324,"text":"that they feel they must use any means necessary"},{"time":100088,"text":"to make others live as they do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103684,"text":"A few months prior to his arrest,"},{"time":105545,"text":"he sat me down and explained that"},{"time":107547,"text":"for the past few weekends, he and some friends"},{"time":110666,"text":"had been going to a shooting range on Long Island"},{"time":112780,"text":"for target practice."},{"time":114963,"text":"He told me I'd be going with him the next morning."},{"time":118653,"text":"We arrived at Calverton Shooting Range,"},{"time":120464,"text":"which unbeknownst to our group was being watched"},{"time":122979,"text":"by the FBI."},{"time":126100,"text":"When it was my turn to shoot,"},{"time":127081,"text":"my father helped me hold the rifle to my shoulder"},{"time":129767,"text":"and explained how to aim at the target"},{"time":131212,"text":"about 30 yards off."},{"time":134353,"text":"That day, the last bullet I shot"},{"time":136696,"text":"hit the small orange light that sat on top of the target"},{"time":139715,"text":"and to everyone's surprise, especially mine,"},{"time":142844,"text":"the entire target burst into flames."},{"time":146818,"text":"My uncle turned to the other men,"},{"time":148719,"text":"and in Arabic said, \"Ibn abuh.\""},{"time":152040,"text":"Like father, like son."},{"time":155795,"text":"They all seemed to get a really\nbig laugh out of that comment,"},{"time":158402,"text":"but it wasn't until a few years later"},{"time":160182,"text":"that I fully understood what\nthey thought was so funny."},{"time":163957,"text":"They thought they saw in me the same destruction"},{"time":166257,"text":"my father was capable of."},{"time":169588,"text":"Those men would eventually be convicted"},{"time":171967,"text":"of placing a van filled with\n1,500 pounds of explosives"},{"time":175940,"text":"into the sub-level parking lot of the\nWorld Trade Center's North Tower,"},{"time":180089,"text":"causing an explosion that killed six people"},{"time":182930,"text":"and injured over 1,000 others."},{"time":186310,"text":"These were the men I looked up to."},{"time":188701,"text":"These were the men I called\nammu, which means uncle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192897,"text":"By the time I turned 19,"},{"time":194668,"text":"I had already moved 20 times in my life,"},{"time":197937,"text":"and that instability during my childhood"},{"time":199966,"text":"didn't really provide an opportunity"},{"time":201440,"text":"to make many friends."},{"time":203321,"text":"Each time I would begin to feel\ncomfortable around someone,"},{"time":206474,"text":"it was time to pack up and move to the next town."},{"time":209643,"text":"Being the perpetual new face in class,"},{"time":211822,"text":"I was frequently the target of bullies."},{"time":214461,"text":"I kept my identity a secret from my classmates"},{"time":216771,"text":"to avoid being targeted,"},{"time":218089,"text":"but as it turns out, being the\nquiet, chubby new kid in class"},{"time":221485,"text":"was more than enough ammunition."},{"time":224002,"text":"So for the most part, I spent my time at home"},{"time":226199,"text":"reading books and watching TV"},{"time":227870,"text":"or playing video games."},{"time":229639,"text":"For those reasons, my social skills were lacking,"},{"time":232509,"text":"to say the least,"},{"time":234759,"text":"and growing up in a bigoted household,"},{"time":236194,"text":"I wasn't prepared for the real world."},{"time":238674,"text":"I'd been raised to judge people"},{"time":240393,"text":"based on arbitrary measurements,"},{"time":242460,"text":"like a person's race or religion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246203,"text":"So what opened my eyes?"},{"time":249354,"text":"One of my first experiences"},{"time":250948,"text":"that challenged this way of thinking"},{"time":253130,"text":"was during the 2000 presidential elections."},{"time":256117,"text":"Through a college prep program,"},{"time":258151,"text":"I was able to take part"},{"time":259285,"text":"in the National Youth Convention in Philadelphia."},{"time":262655,"text":"My particular group's focus was on youth violence,"},{"time":265586,"text":"and having been the victim\nof bullying for most of my life,"},{"time":267937,"text":"this was a subject in which\nI felt particularly passionate."},{"time":272009,"text":"The members of our group came\nfrom many different walks of life."},{"time":276322,"text":"One day toward the end of the convention,"},{"time":278330,"text":"I found out that one of the kids I had befriended"},{"time":281418,"text":"was Jewish."},{"time":283640,"text":"Now, it had taken several days"},{"time":284961,"text":"for this detail to come to light,"},{"time":286604,"text":"and I realized that there was no natural animosity"},{"time":290364,"text":"between the two of us."},{"time":292609,"text":"I had never had a Jewish friend before,"},{"time":295665,"text":"and frankly I felt a sense of pride"},{"time":298474,"text":"in having been able to overcome a barrier"},{"time":300459,"text":"that for most of my life I had been led to believe"},{"time":302743,"text":"was insurmountable."},{"time":305184,"text":"Another major turning point came when"},{"time":307200,"text":"I found a summer job at Busch Gardens,"},{"time":309722,"text":"an amusement park."},{"time":312114,"text":"There, I was exposed to people\nfrom all sorts of faiths and cultures,"},{"time":315010,"text":"and that experience proved to be fundamental"},{"time":317367,"text":"to the development of my character."},{"time":321248,"text":"Most of my life, I'd been taught"},{"time":322508,"text":"that homosexuality was a sin, and by extension,"},{"time":326254,"text":"that all gay people were a negative influence."},{"time":329719,"text":"As chance would have it, I had the opportunity"},{"time":331980,"text":"to work with some of the gay performers"},{"time":333746,"text":"at a show there,"},{"time":335126,"text":"and soon found that many were the kindest,"},{"time":337660,"text":"least judgmental people I had ever met."},{"time":341549,"text":"Being bullied as a kid"},{"time":343792,"text":"created a sense of empathy in me"},{"time":346080,"text":"toward the suffering of others,"},{"time":347626,"text":"and it comes very unnaturally to me"},{"time":349574,"text":"to treat people who are kind"},{"time":351542,"text":"in any other way than how\nI would want to be treated."},{"time":355570,"text":"Because of that feeling, I was able"},{"time":357505,"text":"to contrast the stereotypes I'd been taught as a child"},{"time":361892,"text":"with real life experience and interaction."},{"time":365255,"text":"I don't know what it's like to be gay,"},{"time":367597,"text":"but I'm well acquainted with being judged"},{"time":369260,"text":"for something that's beyond my control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373236,"text":"Then there was \"The Daily Show.\""},{"time":376971,"text":"On a nightly basis, Jon Stewart forced me"},{"time":379243,"text":"to be intellectually honest with\nmyself about my own bigotry"},{"time":382922,"text":"and helped me to realize that a person's race,"},{"time":385239,"text":"religion or sexual orientation"},{"time":388335,"text":"had nothing to do with the quality of one's character."},{"time":392978,"text":"He was in many ways a father figure to me"},{"time":396353,"text":"when I was in desperate need of one."},{"time":399694,"text":"Inspiration can often come\nfrom an unexpected place,"},{"time":403598,"text":"and the fact that a Jewish comedian had done more"},{"time":405983,"text":"to positively influence my worldview"},{"time":408323,"text":"than my own extremist father"},{"time":410170,"text":"is not lost on me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413553,"text":"One day, I had a conversation with my mother"},{"time":415713,"text":"about how my worldview was starting to change,"},{"time":417883,"text":"and she said something to me"},{"time":420559,"text":"that I will hold dear to my heart"},{"time":422090,"text":"for as long as I live."},{"time":425339,"text":"She looked at me with the weary eyes"},{"time":426810,"text":"of someone who had experienced"},{"time":428532,"text":"enough dogmatism to last a lifetime, and said,"},{"time":432590,"text":"\"I'm tired of hating people.\""},{"time":436263,"text":"In that instant, I realized how much negative energy"},{"time":439140,"text":"it takes to hold that hatred inside of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443979,"text":"Zak Ebrahim is not my real name."},{"time":446880,"text":"I changed it when my family decided"},{"time":448915,"text":"to end our connection with my father"},{"time":450580,"text":"and start a new life."},{"time":452942,"text":"So why would I out myself"},{"time":455100,"text":"and potentially put myself in danger?"},{"time":458500,"text":"Well, that's simple."},{"time":460368,"text":"I do it in the hopes that perhaps someone someday"},{"time":464130,"text":"who is compelled to use violence"},{"time":466343,"text":"may hear my story and realize"},{"time":468704,"text":"that there is a better way,"},{"time":471201,"text":"that although I had been subjected"},{"time":472675,"text":"to this violent, intolerant ideology,"},{"time":475431,"text":"that I did not become fanaticized."},{"time":477920,"text":"Instead, I choose to use my experience"},{"time":480557,"text":"to fight back against terrorism,"},{"time":482930,"text":"against the bigotry."},{"time":487321,"text":"I do it for the victims of terrorism"},{"time":490109,"text":"and their loved ones,"},{"time":492291,"text":"for the terrible pain and loss"},{"time":494124,"text":"that terrorism has forced upon their lives."},{"time":497325,"text":"For the victims of terrorism, I will speak out"},{"time":499693,"text":"against these senseless acts"},{"time":502225,"text":"and condemn my father's actions."},{"time":506219,"text":"And with that simple fact, I stand here as proof"},{"time":508862,"text":"that violence isn't inherent in one's religion or race,"},{"time":513520,"text":"and the son does not have to follow"},{"time":516433,"text":"the ways of his father."},{"time":519515,"text":"I am not my father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522305,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525205,"text":"Thank you, everybody. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528864,"text":"Thank you all. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531504,"text":"Thanks a lot. (Applause)"}]}]}